Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.27,0:02:49.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bring it on!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.66,0:02:54.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.62,0:02:59.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We still haven't heard you say it!
