Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.39,0:03:17.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.81,0:03:21.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To live...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.02,0:03:26.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought it was something I dared not wish for.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.03,0:03:32.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one ever let me wish for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.70,0:03:36.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The sea is vast, so someday, definitely...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.87,0:03:40.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...you'll come across friends who'll protect you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.71,0:03:54.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If... it's really okay for me\Nto utter my wish for once...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.05,0:03:57.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.27,0:04:02.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to live!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.43,0:04:07.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take me to the sea with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.88,0:04:31.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys...! I love you guys, dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.75,0:04:34.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.55,0:04:40.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The drawbridge is coming down!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.68,0:04:45.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like they pulled through. Good timing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.66,0:04:47.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.27,0:04:49.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're gonna rescue you for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.73,0:04:54.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The drawbridge is coming down! Go! Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.90,0:04:56.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare those damn pirates?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.82,0:04:58.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're not gonna let it happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.95,0:05:03.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get the trench mortar ready!\NStop the drawbridge! Break it if you have to!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.62,0:05:04.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.24,0:05:14.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The drawbridge stopped coming down?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.01,0:05:17.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare they get in our way?! Damn bastards!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.26,0:05:20.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's doing this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.47,0:05:24.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.68,0:05:26.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Kokoro-san?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.31,0:05:29.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard everything!\NWhat're you guys wasting time for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.98,0:05:32.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wasting time? But the\Nbridge is only halfway down.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.27,0:05:36.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jump with all your might towards the falls!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.90,0:05:39.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The sound of the sea train?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.99,0:05:43.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What's the meaning of that smile?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.18,0:05:54.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.28,0:05:56.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.50,0:06:02.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nooo!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.85,0:06:08.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't gonna take you anyway!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.02,0:06:11.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll never be a pirate!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.89,0:06:12.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will too!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.19,0:06:16.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someday, I'm gonna gather a\Ncrew every bit as good as yours,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.69,0:06:18.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and I'm gonna find the\Ngreatest treasure in the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.90,0:06:22.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and I'm gonna be King of\Nthe Pirates! I'll show you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.29,0:06:29.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I was a kid, I swore that I'd\Ngather a crew and become a pirate...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.37,0:06:32.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...like the pirate who protected me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.88,0:06:36.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're already one of my crew.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.02,0:06:37.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robin...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.67,0:06:41.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like the pirate who protected me,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.55,0:06:44.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll protect you, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.06,0:06:55.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Jump Towards the Falls! Luffy's Feelings!!"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.62,0:07:14.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then take me on your next voyage, Shanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.88,0:07:16.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna be a pirate too!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.59,0:07:20.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As if you could ever be a pirate!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.26,0:07:22.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why not?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.01,0:07:29.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy. Just bein' a good swimmer\Ndoesn't mean you'd make a good pirate.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.02,0:07:32.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm good at fighting too!\NMy punches are like pistols!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.77,0:07:34.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.02,0:07:35.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that mean?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.77,0:07:38.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He means you're too much of a kid, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.44,0:07:40.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously, you're as old as my own kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.03,0:07:43.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not a kid! I'm a grownup!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.41,0:07:46.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now. Don't get so mad.\NHere! Have some juice!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.83,0:07:48.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.16,0:07:52.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See, you are a kid! Ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.29,0:07:53.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That wasn't fair, Shanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.93,0:07:57.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't laugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.75,0:07:59.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stupid cheapskate Shanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.18,0:08:11.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pardon us.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.52,0:08:22.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... So these are "pirates."\NLook pretty damn dumb.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.37,0:08:28.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.24,0:08:35.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're mountain bandits. But we\Nain't here to tear up the place.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.17,0:08:39.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sell us some booze. Ten barrels oughta do.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.32,0:08:44.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. I just ran out of alcohol.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.01,0:08:45.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's odd.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.55,0:08:49.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These pirates seem to be drinking\Nsomething... What is it, water?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.39,0:08:52.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, what they're drinking is the last of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.97,0:08:57.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My apologies. Looks like we\Ndrank the whole place dry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.96,0:08:58.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.56,0:09:02.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can have this, if you'd like.\NIt hasn't been opened yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.46,0:09:14.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's an eight-million-Berry\Nbounty on my head, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.20,0:09:18.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One bottle ain't even enough for\Na bedtime drink! Don't insult me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.09,0:09:23.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now the floor's all wet.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.76,0:09:27.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry about that, Makino-san.\NDo you have a rag?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.05,0:09:30.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'll do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.45,0:09:41.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seems you like to clean. Then maybe\Nyou'll find this more fulfilling.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.82,0:09:46.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not worth our time if they're\Nout of booze. Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.78,0:09:50.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Later, wimps!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.71,0:10:04.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right, Captain? Are you hurt?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.00,0:10:06.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'm fine. No problem at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.97,0:10:13.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He got you good, boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.01,0:10:14.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Talk about lame!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.73,0:10:19.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you laughing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.64,0:10:23.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was so uncool!\NWhy didn't you fight them?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.82,0:10:26.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how many there are\Nor how strong they seem,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.28,0:10:29.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you're not men--or pirates--if you\Nlaugh after something like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.32,0:10:37.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can understand how you feel,\Nbut he only spilled some booze on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.12,0:10:39.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing worth getting mad over.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.04,0:10:40.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.52,0:10:49.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eating out of frustration, Luffy?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.72,0:10:50.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.14,0:10:54.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, what're you eating?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.64,0:11:00.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That box! Did you eat what was in that box?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.14,0:11:00.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.11,0:11:04.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Spit it out! Right now! Every last bite!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.77,0:11:07.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What're you doing, Shanks?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.91,0:11:18.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What... was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.04,0:11:21.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What you ate was the Gum-Gum Fruit!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.79,0:11:23.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Gum-Gum Fruit is known as a Devil Fruit!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.79,0:11:25.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eating it turns your body to rubber,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.67,0:11:29.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and makes you lose the ability\Nto swim for the rest of your life!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.51,0:11:31.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?! No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.93,0:11:33.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You dumbass!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.60,0:11:57.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the idea, boy? People were\Ndrinkin' and havin' a nice time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.43,0:12:00.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit! Apologize! How dare you\Nmake fun of Shanks and his crew?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.88,0:12:06.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did I say something to offend you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.14,0:12:07.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You did! Now apologize!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.42,0:12:09.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayor!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.72,0:12:17.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You see the looks on those pirates' faces?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.22,0:12:21.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He got covered in booze, but didn't\Nsay a word! Talk about pathetic!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.31,0:12:26.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pirates are just a bunch of wimps.\NThey're nothing but talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.56,0:12:27.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.36,0:12:32.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop making fun of Shanks and\Nthe others! They are not wimps!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.82,0:12:34.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.57,0:12:38.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop making fun of Shanks and\Nthe others! You stupid bandits!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.76,0:12:46.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You oughta watch your mouth, boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.91,0:12:51.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one who's ever made me\Nmad has lived to tell the tale.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.88,0:12:53.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.55,0:12:55.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let the boy go! Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.09,0:13:02.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what Luffy has done,\Nnor do I intend to fight with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.35,0:13:04.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're not offended, I'll even pay you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.64,0:13:07.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just, please! Spare the boy's life!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.60,0:13:08.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayor!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.48,0:13:13.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave it to senior citizens\Nto know how the world works.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.44,0:13:15.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But no, it's too late for him now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.86,0:13:18.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, he's made me angry...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.78,0:13:22.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the bad guys! You mountain apes!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.20,0:13:27.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a lost cause, kid. You can\Nregret all this in the next life!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.17,0:13:31.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Luffy!\N--Please! Let him go!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.77,0:13:34.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was wondering why the bar was empty...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.73,0:13:37.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like it's those\Nmountain bandits from before.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.97,0:13:39.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.10,0:13:45.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.40,0:14:10.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you pirates are still here, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.79,0:14:13.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you been scrubbing the\Nvillage clean this whole time?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.04,0:14:14.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.59,0:14:17.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought your punches\Nwere as strong as pistols?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.48,0:14:18.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.23,0:14:23.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I dunno why you're here, but you'd\Nbest leave before you get hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.45,0:14:27.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Any closer and he'll shoot your head off, wimp.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.19,0:14:32.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He said no closer!\NDon't make me blow your head off!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.01,0:14:41.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Put your life on the line.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.83,0:14:42.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.74,0:14:46.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that you've drawn your pistol,\Nput your life on the line.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.00,0:14:48.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell're you talkin' about?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.31,0:14:52.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm saying those aren't for threatening people.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.32,0:15:07.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-Now you've done it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.94,0:15:09.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These bastards fight dirty!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.89,0:15:12.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Dirty?\N--Cut the crap.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.56,0:15:15.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What, do you think you're\Ndealing with saints or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.44,0:15:17.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're looking at pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.10,0:15:20.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! You got nothin' to\Ndo with this in the first place!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.38,0:15:22.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, bandits.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.93,0:15:27.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whether I'm splattered with\Nalcohol or food or even spit on,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.49,0:15:30.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,most of the time I'd just\Nlaugh and forget about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.00,0:15:30.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.33,0:15:33.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what the reason,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.08,0:15:35.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,anyone who hurts my friends has to pay!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.49,0:15:37.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shanks...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.91,0:15:41.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Has to pay, huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.51,0:15:44.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lousy pirates! Kill 'em, men!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.93,0:15:48.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll handle this. Should be easy enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.41,0:16:01.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get cocky, bandit.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.65,0:16:06.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you wanna fight us, then go\Ndrag a warship here or somethin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.95,0:16:08.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.79,0:16:12.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hold on! The kid attacked us!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.22,0:16:14.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are a wanted man.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.08,0:16:17.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.19,0:16:19.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A smokescreen!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.63,0:16:23.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.40,0:16:27.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I made a clean getaway!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.30,0:16:29.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They'll never expect a mountain\Nbandit to escape onto the sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.18,0:16:34.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit! Let me go,\Nyou stupid ape! I hope you die!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.27,0:16:37.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You wish! You're the one who's gonna die!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.27,0:16:40.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, you've made me mad!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.04,0:16:42.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So long!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.20,0:16:45.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit! Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.57,0:16:49.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those guys are scum, but I couldn't\Neven hit them once! Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.79,0:16:58.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry! I got no use for you anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.09,0:17:09.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What the hell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.19,0:17:18.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Help...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.23,0:17:36.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.76,0:17:45.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.11,0:18:09.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm in your debt, Luffy...\NMakino-san told me everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.57,0:18:11.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You fought for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.54,0:18:18.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, don't cry! You're a man!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.91,0:18:21.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But... Shanks...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.83,0:18:24.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your arm!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.25,0:18:27.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's only an arm. It's no big deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.88,0:18:30.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just glad you're alright...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.53,0:18:52.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're leaving, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.98,0:18:56.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. It was a long stay, but now we part ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.96,0:18:58.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bet you'll miss me, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.66,0:19:03.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, yeah, but I won't\Nask you to take me anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.33,0:19:06.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've decided to become\Na pirate on my own now!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.21,0:19:10.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't gonna take you anyway!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.55,0:19:13.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll never be a pirate!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.72,0:19:14.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will too!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.35,0:19:18.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someday, I'm gonna gather a\Ncrew every bit as good as yours,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.90,0:19:21.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and I'm gonna find the\Ngreatest treasure in the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.22,0:19:24.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and I'm gonna be King of\Nthe Pirates! I'll show you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.73,0:19:28.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're gonna surpass us, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.48,0:19:32.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.19,0:19:37.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I'll leave this hat with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.79,0:19:39.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's dear to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.59,0:19:41.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take good care of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.70,0:20:01.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ten years later,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.36,0:20:03.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I sailed out and became a pirate.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.10,0:20:10.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like Shanks protected me,\NI'll protect my friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.20,0:20:21.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nooo!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.17,0:20:28.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just wait, Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.00,0:20:33.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Straw Hat Theater"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.72,0:20:34.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Part 1"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.19,0:20:44.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That bastard...!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.85,0:20:44.97,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,"Usodaba Gang's base of evil"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.18,0:20:47.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That detestable Chopper Man!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.02,0:20:50.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not gonna let him thwart my plans\Nto take over the world anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.32,0:21:03.80,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,"Evil Incarnate, Usodaba"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.86,0:20:53.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Dr. Usodaba, evil incarnate!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.24,0:20:56.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He leads the evil Usodaba Gang\Nand schemes to take over the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.82,0:21:01.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's an evil scientist who produces evil\Nphantoms, monsters, robots--anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.08,0:21:03.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those are some of his underlings behind him.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.17,0:21:08.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll lure him out to my base and\Nwait for him here, ready to strike.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.04,0:21:11.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then, I'll crush him with\Nmy gang's full fighting power!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.74,0:21:12.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Swoosh!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.88,0:21:14.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His weakness is...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.63,0:21:16.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, his assistant, Namifia!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.93,0:21:20.89,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,"Pretty Assistant, Namifia"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.43,0:21:18.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Namifia, a pretty assistant!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.05,0:21:20.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She efficiently manages\NChopper Man's missions.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.31,0:21:22.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, men, go!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.68,0:21:24.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First, bring me a hostage!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.10,0:21:26.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dabada!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.99,0:21:28.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We brought one!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.52,0:21:30.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--'Sup!\N--Hey, you brought him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.31,0:21:38.67,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,"Champion of Justice, Chopper Man"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.52,0:21:33.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Chopper Man, our hero\Nand champion of justice!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.19,0:21:37.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He flies around using his Chopper\Ncape and fights for world peace!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.67,0:21:38.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His weapon is his cuteness!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.04,0:21:48.75,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,"Cute Spark!!"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.41,0:21:43.66,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,With his killer "Cute Spark,"\Nhe can make any enemy's heart melt.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.66,0:21:48.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If that doesn't work, he uses "Chopper\NViolence" to beat the crap out of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.13,0:21:51.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.26,0:21:53.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what's the big deal, relaxing at my base?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.17,0:21:57.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?! What's that big thing in the garden?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.09,0:21:59.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my secret weapon!\NStop checking it out, you jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.39,0:22:01.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I try riding on you?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.58,0:22:02.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.55,0:22:04.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Why are you making\Nfriends with him, Luffybomber?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.89,0:22:17.85,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,"Secret Weapon, Giant Robot,\NGiant Luffybomber"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.43,0:22:08.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Giant Luffybomber, a giant\Nrobot and their secret weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.40,0:22:10.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a giant robot that's fifty meters tall.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.56,0:22:14.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When Usodaba comes on board,\Nit becomes your worst, strongest enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.03,0:22:15.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Special traits: It can speak.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.82,0:22:17.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Personality: It does its own thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.96,0:22:35.67,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,"Rice Ball Monster, Zorokiller"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.08,0:22:31.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the rice ball monster, Zorokiller!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.71,0:22:33.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When he demands rice balls,\Nif you don't have any,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.75,0:22:35.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he gets angry and says, "Make sure\Nyou have some from now on!"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.67,0:22:41.64,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,"Flower Monster, Robiflowern"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.01,0:22:38.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the flower monster,\NRobiflowern. She's an evil woman
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.38,0:22:41.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who's been defeated by Chopper Man's\Nkiller "Cute Spark" time after time.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.64,0:22:48.10,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,"Naughty Monster, Sanjiropus"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.72,0:22:43.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the naughty monster, Sanjiropus.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.31,0:22:46.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He insists that he isn't naughty, but he's\Nalways thinking about naughty stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.48,0:22:48.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He shows no mercy to guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.10,0:22:52.55,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Usodaba Gang's Evil Three"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.65,0:22:50.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They are the Usodaba Gang's Evil Three.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.88,0:22:52.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They have nothing to do\Nwith this story, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.69,0:22:56.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thus, the evil gang has been wiped out.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.37,0:22:57.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.82,0:22:59.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're cool, Luffybomber!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.60,0:23:00.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Darn straight I am!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.70,0:23:05.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chopper Man! There's trouble\Nin one of the eastern towns!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.16,0:23:10.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! I'll head there in Luffybomber,\Nthe giant robot I obtained the other day!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.71,0:23:12.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--It's not here!\N--I sold it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.54,0:23:14.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What?!\N--Go! Go! Our Chopper Man!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.92,0:23:17.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fight for world peace!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.57,0:23:29.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Don't worry, Robin-kun.\NY-You've got us on your side.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.06,0:23:32.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He says, while trembling in his boots.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.10,0:23:34.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm just trembling with anticipation!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.02,0:23:37.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah? Well then, let's hurry up and take\Ncare of these World Government guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.90,0:23:40.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then we'll rescue Robin-kun without fail!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.57,0:23:42.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.20,0:23:45.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Ways of Men!\NZoro's Techniques, Usopp's Dream"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.71,0:23:48.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
