Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.57,0:00:15.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.57,0:00:17.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wealth, fame, power...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.53,0:00:19.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gold Roger, the King of the Pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.32,0:00:21.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,attained everything this world has to offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.33,0:00:25.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The words he uttered just before\Nhis death drove people to the seas.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.04,0:00:28.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My treasure? If you want it, you can have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.83,0:00:32.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Find it! I left everything\Nthis world has to offer there!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.92,0:00:39.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so men head for the Grand Line\Nin pursuit of their dreams!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.68,0:00:42.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world has truly\Nentered a Great Pirate Era!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.81,0:00:49.13,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to gather up\Nall our dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.13,0:00:54.94,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,and set out in search\Nof something to find
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.94,0:00:56.40,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,ONE PIECE!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.07,0:01:06.71,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Compasses only cause delays
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.71,0:01:12.46,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Delirious with fever,\NI take the helm
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.46,0:01:24.60,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,If the dusty treasure map has\Nbeen verified, it's not a legend!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.60,0:01:30.23,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,When it comes to personal storms,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.23,0:01:35.61,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,simply ride aboard\Nsomeone else's biorhythm
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.61,0:01:38.03,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,and pretend it isn't there!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.20,0:01:44.83,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to gather up\Nall our dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.83,0:01:50.34,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,and set out in search\Nof something to find
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.34,0:01:56.60,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,A coin in my pocket,\Nand do you wanna be my friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.61,0:02:01.95,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We are, We are on the cruise!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.96,0:02:03.87,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We are!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.89,0:02:10.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The drawbridge is coming down!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.07,0:02:15.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like they pulled through. Good timing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.29,0:02:22.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm trembling with anticipation!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.05,0:02:23.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.49,0:02:26.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're gonna rescue you for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.54,0:02:30.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lower that bridge already.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.42,0:02:32.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He looks evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.34,0:02:41.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hear you're a bad guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.51,0:02:43.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you still here?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.18,0:02:47.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Being stuck out here for all to see...\NAre you really strong at all?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.18,0:02:48.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mind your own business!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.06,0:02:55.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously... just because I teamed\Nup with Luffy, I've come this far.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.82,0:03:07.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Ways of Men!\NZoro's Techniques, Usopp's Dream"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.01,0:03:30.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're still as weak as ever, Zoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.43,0:03:33.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I promised her...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.15,0:03:38.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't afford to die in a place like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.08,0:03:53.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You again? You sure have lots of free time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.08,0:03:55.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll untie you, so join my crew!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.75,0:03:56.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.92,0:03:59.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm looking for people to join my pirate crew.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.25,0:04:05.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forget it! Me, stooping to a\Ncriminal's level?! Screw that!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.76,0:04:07.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with being a pirate?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.72,0:04:10.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pirates are despicable! As if I'd wanna be one!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.10,0:04:15.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, come on! You're already\Nknown as an evil bounty hunter!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.60,0:04:20.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,People can say whatever they want,\Nbut I ain't done anything I regret.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.53,0:04:26.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will live through this\Nand accomplish what I want!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.92,0:04:28.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.28,0:04:31.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I've decided you're gonna join me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.83,0:04:33.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quit deciding on your own!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.50,0:04:34.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hear you use swords.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.58,0:04:39.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. But that stupid son took my stuff...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.58,0:04:41.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--I'll go get it back for you!\N--What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.80,0:04:44.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So if you want your sword, join my crew!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.89,0:04:46.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're really getting on my nerves!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.14,0:04:51.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is he planning to bust into the base by himself?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.39,0:04:53.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After him! Don't let him escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.60,0:04:56.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain! There's someone\Nin the crucifixion yard!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.14,0:04:57.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.86,0:05:04.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's one traitor after the other...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.36,0:05:08.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please escape, Zoro-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.41,0:05:11.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be killed for doing that, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.12,0:05:13.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't stand to watch\Nthe Navy like this anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.83,0:05:17.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to be an honorable marine!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.91,0:05:21.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop! I can't escape! I only got ten days until--
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.88,0:05:23.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to be executed tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.30,0:05:25.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.30,0:05:29.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Helmeppo never once intended\Nto honor your agreement!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.80,0:05:34.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So Luffy-san got angry and punched him!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.60,0:05:35.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He did?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.89,0:05:39.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Navy is after Luffy-san now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.73,0:05:43.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't ask you to be a pirate.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.02,0:05:47.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But please, help Luffy-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.86,0:05:54.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy-san is the only one who can save you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.66,0:06:01.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I think you're also the only\None who can save Luffy-san now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.67,0:06:05.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,End of the line!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.14,0:06:16.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is some interesting\Nstuff you guys've pulled!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.93,0:06:23.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Were you two and that straw hat kid\Nplannin' a coup or something?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.40,0:06:25.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've always fought alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.48,0:06:30.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unlike arrogant bastards like you\Nwho use soldiers as cronies!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.70,0:06:32.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roronoa Zoro...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.74,0:06:34.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you dare underestimate me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.43,0:06:40.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You may be strong, but before my\Nauthority, you're as good as scum!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.84,0:06:42.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aim!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.96,0:06:44.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.42,0:06:50.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...can't afford to die here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.64,0:06:55.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're still as weak as ever, Zoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.13,0:07:00.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.52,0:07:01.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Rocket!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.48,0:07:02.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.77,0:07:08.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What are you--?!\N--Luffy-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.12,0:07:09.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.61,0:07:16.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That doesn't work!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.16,0:07:23.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you I was strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.79,0:07:26.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Who the hell are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.92,0:07:30.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Monkey D. Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.44,0:07:32.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The man who's gonna be King of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.72,0:07:34.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The King of the Pirates?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.80,0:07:37.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you even know what that means?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.39,0:07:40.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,King of the Pirates is King of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.81,0:07:42.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are there any other meanings?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.06,0:07:50.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was shocked, too! But Luffy-san\Nis serious! That's how he is!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.44,0:07:52.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He intends to become the King of the Pirates
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.44,0:07:57.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and obtain this world's\Nultimate treasure... the One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.66,0:08:02.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here's your treasure!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.91,0:08:06.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which is yours? I couldn't tell,\Nso I brought three of 'em.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.75,0:08:10.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All three are mine. I use the Three-Sword Style.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.34,0:08:14.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll take 'em, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.51,0:08:18.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we fight together now, you'll be\Na government-defying villain!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.93,0:08:22.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you prefer that, or being\Nkilled by the Navy like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.68,0:08:24.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you, the devil's son?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.93,0:08:30.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, whatever. I'll be your pirate,\Nif I'm just gonna die here instead!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.23,0:08:34.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurray! So you'll join my crew?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.69,0:08:37.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! Woo-hoo! This is great! Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.28,0:08:40.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! Now untie these stupid ropes already!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.62,0:08:42.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What... is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.12,0:08:43.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He flung the bullets back!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.37,0:08:47.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's no ordinary human, that Straw Hat...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.04,0:08:50.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Must've eaten one of\Nthose rumored Devil Fruits!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.67,0:08:51.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A Devil Fruit?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.96,0:08:53.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.38,0:08:55.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! These knots are tight!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.76,0:08:57.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Quit wastin' time!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.63,0:09:02.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter who they are, everyone\Nwho opposes me gets executed!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.06,0:09:04.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If guns won't work, then chop them to death!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.69,0:09:11.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh, that's weird! It got tighter instead!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.36,0:09:12.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me a damn sword!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.04,0:09:16.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.16,0:09:27.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roronoa Zoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.25,0:09:30.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.36,0:09:33.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Move and you're dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.05,0:09:36.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Too scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.80,0:09:43.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be a pirate. I promise you that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.93,0:09:47.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm officially a criminal,\Nnow that I've fought the Navy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.73,0:09:52.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'll tell you this right now.\NI'm only going to fulfill my ambition!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.83,0:09:53.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ambition?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.19,0:09:57.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To be the world's greatest swordsman!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.44,0:10:00.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I wind up having to give that up,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.82,0:10:04.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you'd better accept responsibility\Nand apologize to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.12,0:10:08.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world's greatest swordsman?\NThat sounds great!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.62,0:10:12.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The King of the Pirates would\Nneed no less than that on his crew!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.63,0:10:14.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure talk big.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.54,0:10:17.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At this point, whether it's\Nas a criminal or whatever else,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.30,0:10:19.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will spread my name throughout the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.18,0:10:24.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you standing around for?!\NSlaughter them this instant!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.89,0:10:27.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Duck, Zoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.52,0:10:32.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum Whip!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.02,0:10:37.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You did it! Incredible!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.82,0:10:39.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.99,0:10:42.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I ate the Gum-Gum Fruit.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.78,0:10:43.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum Fruit?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.45,0:10:46.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A rubber person!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.03,0:10:48.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So he does have Devil Fruit powers!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.50,0:10:50.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain! We don't stand a chance against them!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.87,0:10:52.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These guys are crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.33,0:10:54.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't even handle Zoro by himself!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.21,0:10:59.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a direct order!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.01,0:11:00.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone who spouted weakness just now
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.88,0:11:02.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,must now shoot themselves in the head!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.84,0:11:05.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no need for weakling soldiers!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.52,0:11:11.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These troops are mental!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.85,0:11:13.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.31,0:11:17.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Crush this navy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.57,0:11:31.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rankless, low-status bums have\Nno right whatsoever to defy me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.37,0:11:35.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am Navy Captain "Axe-Hand" Morgan!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.38,0:11:37.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Luffy! Nice to meetcha!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.04,0:11:39.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.56,0:11:50.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-The captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.22,0:11:53.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,R-Runt...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.76,0:11:56.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.99,0:11:58.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.03,0:12:02.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C-Captain Morgan is...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.11,0:12:06.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...being trounced completely...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.41,0:12:12.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you call yourself a navy?!\NYou've destroyed Coby's dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.87,0:12:16.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it, Straw Hat! Check this out!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.09,0:12:21.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I said hold it! Are you stupid?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.59,0:12:24.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pay attention! I have a hostage here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.88,0:12:26.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Helmeppo-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.43,0:12:27.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.93,0:12:35.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you value this guy's life, don't move!\NOne move and I'll shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.80,0:12:47.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy-san! I don't want to get in\Nyour way! Even if it means dying!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.14,0:12:50.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.47,0:12:54.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give it up, stupid son!\NCoby really is ready to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.87,0:12:59.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't move! I told you not to move! I-I'll shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.03,0:13:02.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Behind you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.30,0:13:03.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.63,0:13:08.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am Navy Captain "Axe-Hand" Morgan!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.59,0:13:10.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad! Kill him, quick!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.76,0:13:14.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Pistol!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.02,0:13:18.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.66,0:13:28.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zoro.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.15,0:13:31.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My pleasure, Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.45,0:14:01.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The drawbridge stopped coming down?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.93,0:14:04.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare they get in our way?! Damn bastards!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.07,0:14:07.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's doing this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.95,0:14:12.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do not worry, Robin-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.10,0:14:15.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just trembling with anticipation!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.78,0:14:19.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We will... rescue you for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.33,0:14:23.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a whole bunch of bad guys, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.08,0:14:24.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Scared" is written all over your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.26,0:14:30.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,M-Me, scared?! I'm perfectly okay\Nwith lots of bad guys or whatever!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.43,0:14:34.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I'm Captain Usopp,\Nbrave warrior of the sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.26,0:14:41.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit! Dammit! This isn't a show!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.19,0:14:43.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These are Klahadore's\Npirates we're dealing with!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.40,0:14:46.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I'm scared! What's wrong with that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.48,0:14:51.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want your sympathy!\NYou guys can leave! Leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.36,0:14:55.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We ain't laughing! We're helping\N'cause we think you're honorable!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.90,0:14:59.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As if we'd risk our lives because of sympathy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.17,0:15:08.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... You guys...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.15,0:15:10.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usopp!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.22,0:15:17.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Dammit...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.25,0:15:21.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... can't... move...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.60,0:15:24.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Though, even if you did catch up with Jango,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.77,0:15:27.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you'd be no match for him anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.56,0:15:30.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This way is probably safest for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.23,0:15:32.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I am no match...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.66,0:15:40.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I am no match for him...\NI will protect them!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.06,0:15:44.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm captain of the Usopp Pirates...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.33,0:15:47.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and a brave warrior of the sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.89,0:15:53.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you lay a finger on the village!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.14,0:15:58.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What's with him?\N--He's yellin' somethin'!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.47,0:16:00.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Check it out, he's cryin'!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.80,0:16:15.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's so funny?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.40,0:16:19.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.12,0:16:23.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me and Usopp are gonna chase\Nthat hypno-freak! That a problem?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.52,0:16:24.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nope! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.40,0:16:31.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like you're one step too late, Haramaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.63,0:16:32.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't say so!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.88,0:16:39.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! That branch was in the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.13,0:16:42.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.06,0:16:42.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usopp-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.13,0:16:44.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Special Attack: Exploding Star!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.72,0:16:55.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you are taking to the ocean, Usopp-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.26,0:17:00.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I've decided to get going\Nbefore I start to change my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.57,0:17:03.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't stop me, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.75,0:17:06.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't. I could just tell somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.31,0:17:09.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's kind of sad, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.54,0:17:11.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The next time I come to this village,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.88,0:17:15.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll tell you adventure stories that\Nseem even more lie-like than lies!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.77,0:17:18.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! I look forward to it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.59,0:17:23.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys take care, too!\NLet's meet again sometime!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.71,0:17:26.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--How come?\N--Huh? How come?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.84,0:17:29.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, you're antisocial...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.35,0:17:33.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be a pirate too, so we'll\Nmeet on the high seas eventually!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.68,0:17:36.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you talkin' about? Get on already.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.58,0:17:39.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Eh?!\N--We're friends now, aren't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.94,0:17:50.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.16,0:17:53.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I get to be captain, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.38,0:17:56.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be dumb! I'm the captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.25,0:18:14.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, pirates! What're you\Nguys wasting time for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.61,0:18:17.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wasting time? But the\Nbridge is only halfway down.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.71,0:18:20.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Halfway is good enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.55,0:18:22.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be there in four seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.14,0:18:26.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jump with all your might towards the falls!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.25,0:18:30.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that Granny? What does she mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.25,0:18:32.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know. But she said\Njump towards the falls.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.80,0:18:37.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The sound of the sea train?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.25,0:18:41.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What's the meaning of that smile?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.28,0:18:52.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.24,0:18:54.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.11,0:19:02.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nooo!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.04,0:19:10.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Straw Hat Theater"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.77,0:19:11.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Part 2"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.01,0:19:21.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"A report on Luffy's eating habits\Nbefore Sanji joined the gang."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.14,0:19:26.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is "On-Location Tsubaki," a crooked\Nreporter who'll help us on this report.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.62,0:19:27.18,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,"His favorite words:
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.51,0:19:29.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His favorite words are:\N"I'm so happy that words fail me."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.18,0:19:31.02,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,"His favorite words:\N'I'm so happy that words fail me'"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.97,0:19:34.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Err... This is On-Location Tsubaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.85,0:19:37.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy, you set sail all by yourself, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.45,0:19:41.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell everyone how an idiot like you survived.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.61,0:19:42.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.69,0:19:46.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I took lots of meat and water that I got\Nin the village with me when I set sail.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.93,0:19:49.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I ate them all right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.75,0:19:51.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so dumbfounded that words fail me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.54,0:19:55.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, after that I was starving\Nand thirsty. It was really tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.71,0:20:00.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I was saved by eating mushrooms\Nand stuff that someone left in the boat.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.31,0:20:02.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, the mushrooms just grew\Nbecause of the ample humidity.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.27,0:20:08.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But then, big fish would sometimes\Njump out of the sea, trying to eat me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.73,0:20:10.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I beat them up and...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.31,0:20:12.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ate them?! You could've died.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.73,0:20:14.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It sounds like you were living hand to mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.23,0:20:17.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it was okay! I had confidence in myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.98,0:20:21.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey, hey... That's so\Npowerful that words fail me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.63,0:20:25.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Err... And then, that stupid\NZoro became a crew member.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.25,0:20:28.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I can't expect much from you, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.39,0:20:31.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You both are idiots. How were\Nyou able to make it this far?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.55,0:20:35.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I set sail before he did,\Nso I was more experienced.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.64,0:20:37.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was used to sailing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.84,0:20:40.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our captain is like this, so I had\Nto be the one who got it together.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.41,0:20:47.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big fish would sometimes jump out of the sea,\Ntrying to eat us. So I beat them up and...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.51,0:20:50.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been caught in the chains of\Ndisappointment and can't move.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.68,0:20:52.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, you could've\Nstarved to death then,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.72,0:20:55.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,which could've led to the\Nend of your adventures, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.48,0:21:00.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. But if we had died, that would mean\Nwe weren't man enough to make it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.44,0:21:03.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey, hey... That's so manly that words fail me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.18,0:21:07.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, then. Come on,\NNami the gangster woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.23,0:21:11.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really, I was surprised by their lack\Nof planning or any sense of danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.60,0:21:17.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I managed the food\Nafter we set sail together...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.13,0:21:19.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...while being careful about properly preserving
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.66,0:21:21.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,cheese, bread, dried meat, etc. and water.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.88,0:21:24.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They might've died if it wasn't for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.99,0:21:26.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.68,0:21:28.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...they owe me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.43,0:21:32.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey, hey... That smile is so\Nscheming that words fail me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.57,0:21:35.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, we have Usopp the scaredy-cat\Nwho was next to join the gang.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.00,0:21:37.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Straw Hats finally got a bigger ship
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.27,0:21:40.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,by obtaining the Going Merry when\Nyou left your village, didn't you,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.27,0:21:41.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,even though you're all idiots?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.48,0:21:44.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. I want them to\Nappreciate me for that first.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.68,0:21:46.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't you who gave it to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.62,0:21:47.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's right. It was Kaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.87,0:21:50.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was because I was good\Nfriends with Kaya, wasn't it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.39,0:21:53.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you wanna fight, do it later.\NDid something change in your life?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.99,0:21:57.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah! Usopp is good at fishing,\Nso we ate quite a bit of fish.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.16,0:22:01.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the fish you catch,\Nlike sauries and sardines, are small.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.48,0:22:05.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You dummy! I like seasonal fish\Nbetter than the meat of sea monsters!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.56,0:22:09.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We had a kitchen, so I\Ncooked for you guys, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.60,0:22:12.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usopp's got lots of seasonings for some reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.46,0:22:15.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To tell you the truth, Nami's homemade\Nfood was quite good, but it wasn't free.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.75,0:22:17.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So we never asked her to cook again.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.37,0:22:19.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm an expensive woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.39,0:22:22.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are devils everywhere in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.55,0:22:29.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And now, we finally have a damn filthy\Nman who always says "damn, damn."
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.40,0:22:34.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To be honest, I wanna cook just\Nfor Nami-san. My hobby is Nami-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.69,0:22:35.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since Sanji joined us,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.87,0:22:40.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,meals have become something\Nwe really look forward to.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.06,0:22:44.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we catch things like birds or fish,\Nhe'll turn them into really yummy food!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.51,0:22:48.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since he's a pro, he considers\Nnutritional balance, too, so that's helpful!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.13,0:22:51.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Mellorine! Mellorine! Love hurricane!\N--I was finally able to focus\Non my job as a navigator.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.93,0:22:54.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the only redeeming trait\Nyou have, so you can do your best.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.77,0:22:55.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What'd you say, you bastard?!
